subtitles.dialogue_text: Good Luck, Chihiro We'll meet again

will break the spell and the a ttendants will see you

I'm sorry, I took a brea th

0r maybe you' d like the worst,

Of him? I sure hope not

Thank you He's got a thorn stuck in him
